        <item>
            <title>【教学】AI 执相修图 Google Gemini 2.0 Flash，输入文字即可 PS 图片毋须技术</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/14/google-gemini-ai-2/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=google-gemini-ai-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/14/google-gemini-ai-2/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 11:56:52 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Google Gemini]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1297625</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Google Gemini 2.0 Flash 推出了一段时间，但一直仅限部分人测试，最近 Google 终于开放。目前 Gemini 2.0 flash 已推出 Experimental 版本，能够生成图片，基本上你输入指令就可以替你修改图片。现在就让小编和大家一起试玩这个新功能吧！</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297629" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025031451511-467x580.jpg" alt="" width="467" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025031451511-467x580.jpg 467w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025031451511.jpg 724w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 467px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲一句即可帮你改颜色</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297671" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025031463541-466x580.jpg" alt="" width="466" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025031463541-466x580.jpg 466w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025031463541.jpg 723w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 466px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲也可生成可爱卡通</p><h2>需求</h2><p>VPN</p><h2>Step 1 登入 Google 帐户</h2><p>开启 VPN 之后，点击下面连结进入 Google Gemini 2.0 页面，再点击「Try in Google AI Studio」，然后你就可以登入你的 Google 帐户。</p><p>连结：<a href="https://deepmind.google/technologies/gemini/flash/">https://deepmind.google/technologies/gemini/flash/</a></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297630" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025031451945-694x371.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="371" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025031451945-694x371.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025031451945.jpg 1097w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲点击「Try in Google AI Studio」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297631" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_5_21_31-694x353.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="353" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_5_21_31-694x353.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_5_21_31.jpg 929w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲登入 Google 帐户</p><br /><b>
]]>
